{"tid":839550,"cid":31,"subCid":7,"title":"「新手改歌」明天應更好應更天晴，一張臉微微笑似更精靈","createTime":"2018-09-28T04:30:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-28T08:23:42.000Z","uid":71508,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"90b3f239dd94b68fdbf8007ffdeb6fbc413bdc01","tid":839550,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T04:30:00.000Z","msg":"明天應更好應更天晴<br />\n一張臉微微笑似更精靈 <br />\n從今天放低心裡女神<br />\n銀包能同時擴闊會更溫馨 <br />\n<br />\nOn99 on9每天 <br />\n返工heahea 又過一天 <br />\n有女照食 最愛叫囂 <br />\n最愛食過橋 樂趣不少 <br />\n<br />\n我有問題 四個問題 <br />\n想解答 IT狗 IT狗 無閉翳 <br />\n開OT 開OT<br />\n心要齊 不介懷冇補水<br />\n<br />\n你亂嚟 咪亂嚟 <br />\n唔專心失誤出錯唔抵 <br />\n心中有女神<br />\n猜猜那女神<br />\n不需要你請 不如一齊食譚仔<br />\n<br />\n決心要集合齊人<br />\n迎接那打風永不擔心 <br />\n人人要向一份工逐步前行 <br />\n時時要無懼老細不分心<br />\n天天都看到女神<br />\n晴天日日黎<br />\n<br />\nHello又係我<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n今次已經改善咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/devil.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/devil.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2dbaa76137a2a4bc5ff614f181fa08a323bba9d7","tid":839550,"uid":136038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T04:38:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79d237d4e66c71dd54ebab1aeb1e50f95d94362e","tid":839550,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2dbaa76137a2a4bc5ff614f181fa08a323bba9d7","tid":839550,"uid":136038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T04:38:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/a